Type of Feat: Class
Specifics: Starting at 3rd level, once per day as a standard action, a blightlord may attempt a melee touch attack to infect a victim with the blight. This disease (DC 10 + blightlord class level + Wisdom modifier) deals d4 Constitution and d4 Charisma damage. At 5th, 7th, and 9th level, the blightlord gains one more use of this power per day.
Use: Selected.